Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.81,0:23:23.27,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}做想做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:50.01,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}蹴鞠头儿再袭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有惊无险嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  圭子  考得怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,65分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来都准备好亮红灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样还算过得去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  圭子你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一百
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总共一百分你全拿到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说「百发百中」了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说没有失误了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说很完美了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无趣的分数
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么擅长计算的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去当个计算器好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这计算器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不必说得这么过分吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此相比  65分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才像是人该得的分数
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:03:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和计算器比试也太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有棋逢对手的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考得怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊  头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想向我挑战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？头儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你打算用什么分数来和我较量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是说出来听听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  我会轻而易举地击败你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆些说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  不…我不是想较量什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,66分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不必说得那么过分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才说了什么很过分的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没输
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:41.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs27}迄今战绩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:42.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs27}一胜一负
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你之间的战绩才不过是一胜一负
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:46.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我什么时候输的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以英语考试的成绩来决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…可以倒是可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp128}　{\fsp1}Penalty{\r}\N那么来约定一下处罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁输了就得装狗  如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说夏奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  好的  那就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别想溜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你乖乖伸爪子的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:06.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：原文「お手」，训狗用的口令）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这就差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便问下  圭子你考得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？呃…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去美国过活算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,61分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是个人情味儿十足的美妙分数
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可刚才65分也还是输了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:39.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs27}篡改
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来  那家伙刚才是66分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:49.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs27}篡改  Ⅱ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学  怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊  藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先让我看看你的分数吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:04:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,69分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你还改了两次分数…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？我赢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比试这才开始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:23.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs27}篡改  Ⅲ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:28.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(880,870)}一百
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:40.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs27}篡改  Ⅳ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:45.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(960,920)}一百
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:52.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(910,920)\fs27}午休（午餐供应）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:08.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fs27}篡改  Ⅴ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:12.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(960,920)}一百
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又…又输了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改了这么多次分数还…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我赢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  说好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸爪子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学  那可是脚…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然叫做「前脚」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么爪子也是脚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚也是脚！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想冒昧一问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近  在学校的考试成绩如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这虾黄酱口味的饼干很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么搪塞我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为觉得这话题发展下去准没什么好结果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可…不见得…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙实在太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为只要不是一百就有人情味儿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人家的牛奶喝个精光还反过来说我「差劲」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没什么好结果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就一笔勾销了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么一笔勾销了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有输
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是考试成绩不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是包含人间温情的美好的分数
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别因为自己考了97分就得意洋洋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子她还考了一百呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你又是多少分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我喝光你的牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么样  见识到我的可怕之处了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp254}　{\fsp1}Cream Stew{\r}\N春香姐姐可是说了今晚要做奶油杂烩的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上还满满的一盒到傍晚就一干二净了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概姐姐她也没想到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我去买总行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子里的牛奶晃荡得好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶这蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎么着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为千秋你总是狡诈地学啊学的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说什么狡诈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:09:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你分数就那么差吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不是差了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是一个通情达理真心实意的分数
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指望以抱佛脚换来好分数的想法本身就有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就只能说出这么大众化的意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来娶你的男人还真是不幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:27.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这种大众化意见所掩埋的新婚生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:32.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不可能会有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别凭自己的妄想断言别人的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就单说做饭也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就无法做出让人感动的饭菜来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能感动也无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你的夫婿就将这么结束没有感动的不幸的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做出来对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:11:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非比寻常的你应该能做出让人感动的饭菜来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你去做给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯  让你品尝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时  能够创造出新奇食物的不是常识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是那瞬间的灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬间的灵感上回孕育出了惨不忍睹的奶油杂烩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  对不起  已经等不及了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们做了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Gratin　{\r}\N奶汁烤菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天麸罗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:43.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：日式食品，裹上面粉后油炸的鱼虾之类）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Paella{\r}\N还是西班牙海鲜饭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你做奶油杂烩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买牛奶来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜者  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一介奶油杂烩也能使人心荡神驰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？什么时候睡着的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:12:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  想报仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然趁我睡着时偷袭  太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂正正地来比试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一堂课要改去音乐教室上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你却在这儿睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想叫醒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可看你睡得很舒服就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:17.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（下节课  音乐教室）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真是很可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  也无所谓就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次好像并没有很好地传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就直说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.76,0:13:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋大小姐回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何事  甚是吵嚷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些事想和您谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在学校头儿对我说「我很喜欢你」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前他不还给我写了情书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是喜欢你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我太得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  他是在什么情况下对你说的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  想报仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在教室里睡着了  而他好像想偷袭我的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我就对他说「堂堂正正地来比试吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说你因为在睡梦中被偷袭而情绪不稳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又因为他出人意料的话语而心神不宁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致思考回路短路了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是怎么一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的大脑在听到「很喜欢」的那一刻就停止工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头儿后来应该还说了些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一说  好像确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从当时的情况推测的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕当时他是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你那架势满是破绽」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:23.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：此句发音的前半部分和「很喜欢」这句一样）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太难为情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然三番两次地会错意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到饥渴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在追求什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那所谓的告白之类酸酸甜甜的什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这么一来就清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清楚我们应该采取何种对策了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来  今天足球部有练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一节是数学课哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  什么作业？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你好  打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买饮料回来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  千秋  欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就是藤冈啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个头儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么头儿会在咱家？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是想和他大干一场然后取而代之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望能避免无谓的纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天不是咖喱做多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？怎么稀得像水一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp32}　{\fsp1}Curry Roux{\r}\N再加些咖喱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？这次就太稠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能弄稀一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？觉得又稀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加些咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又太稠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只好加水了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太稀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太稠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么最后会做出三大锅咖喱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用做多了的咖喱和头儿套关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一石二鸟的好法子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他就这么跟着你来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本还以为南同学讨厌我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像并不是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还请我上家里来吃晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离一下子就拉近了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  给你茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:00.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（举止可疑）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人一定在打什么鬼主意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  说笑的说笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说啊  春香姐姐做的咖喱可是非常好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  有意见你倒是别吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  剩下两大锅你打算自己吃完？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  是小的出言不逊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈同学不是个挺好的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  他居然会是头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是有什么误会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且该怎么说好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他给人的感觉酷似爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:49.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸给人的感觉是那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宫同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师～！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宫同学！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师和二宫同学后续如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请下周继续收看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已经这么晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多得回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  这可不像千秋你的作风哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想说的话就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.18,0:20:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那儿是我的位子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来  藤冈同学参加了什么社团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我参加了足球部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  足球部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢什么位置呢  是主力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧  前场的任何位置都可以踢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺厉害的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种温暖的气氛是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算不光是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连春香和千秋也要一并拉拢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一石三鸟的作战方案？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我出去！
